Your Makevar.site is incorrect.  Replace
  CXX11 = $CXX
with
  CXX11 = $(CXX)

$CXX only expands the macro 'C', not 'CXX'.  Since C is not defined $CXX
expands to XX.

Bill Dunlap
TIBCO Software
